title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J Kaiser Convention Center on 1988-03-16
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Stagger Lee, Walkin' Blues, Candyman, Queen Jane Approximately, Big Boss Man, Cassidy, Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Playin' In The Band-> Jam-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> All Along The Watchtower-> Morning Dew, E: Touch Of Grey

reviews.review_text: WOW OMG what a amazing audience recording!! Wow this is just as good as it gets. Fantastic show too, i was there. Jerry grilled fish on a Weber grill during setbreaks on the the side of the stage. Thank you big time to taper for the UL.

wow is rite Holy cow where did this one come from? This has to be a front of board. AMAZING SOUND feels like the boys are in your face.  Dam not sure it sounded this good that day in the Kaiser itself. You did an outstanding job recording this one.   SMOKIN SMOKIN SMOKIN.... DON'T GIVE MANY 5 STARS THIS ONE GETS 5 DUE TO SOUND ALONE.   Set list doesn't hurt.
Best Aud source Great show.  Very nice recording.  Better than Schoeps version.
